{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Publicly urge the US Government to end its oil & economic embargo against Cuba",
        "additional_details": "Cuba is facing severe fuel shortages and blackouts, worsened by the US embargo and blocked oil shipments. We believe the UK should use its diplomatic frameworks to raise concern about the humanitarian impact and support efforts to ensure essential supplies reach Cuba.",
        "background": "We ask the UK Government to publicly call for the end to the US\u2019 economic embargo and measures preventing oil from reaching Cuba, and to raise this through diplomatic channels, including the United Nations and the UK\u2013Cuba Political Dialogue and Cooperation Agreement.",
